wikipedia_page.main: Gayle Williamson (born c. 1980, Dollingstown, Northern Ireland) is a model and the 2002 Miss Northern Ireland and the 2002 Miss United Kingdom title holders. She was also a contestant in the 2002 Miss World beauty contest.
